# Implementation Plan: {{ title }}


## Goal

The main winding was of the normal lotus-o-delta type placed in panendermic semi-boloid slots
in the stator, every seventh conductor being connected by a non-reversible tremie pipe to the
differential girdlespring on the up-end of the grammeters.


